  "special": {
    "title": "Sink me!",
    "description": "On impact, creates a secondary projectile that rises vertically then splits into five pellets in a star pattern.\n\nPellets use the weapon's normal stats and can hit twice: first at full damage, then again at 50% damage. The gap between hits depends on projectile speed.\n\nSplash damage benefits from Reaper but not grenade damage bonuses, and the rifle has increased sniper critical damage."
  },
  "notes": "Usually named \"Captain Scarlett's Pimpernel\"; any accessory can change the prefix.\n\nA Gentleman's slag version keeps the bonus crit effect even if not shown on the card. Split pellets take full amp damage.\n\nGaige: Close Enough ricochets spawn pellets at the enemy hit point. Salvador: in off-hand, pellets use main-hand damage/element; if the main-hand mag is empty they also gain Money Shot scaling. Pellets cannot hit the user.\n\nProjectile speed affects pellet spread and hit spacing; Vel0city and Accelerate alter this.\n\nCan trigger B0re; B0re, Chain Reaction and The Nth Degree can re-trigger repeatedly on grouped targets.",
